					Segment To Create

KEY:
ovl	- code overlay
btxt - background textures
atxt - animation textures

;--------------------------------------------------------------
Subway & Street:
Overlay Code:	sbst_ovl
Bkgd Textures:	sbst_btxt
Bkgd Animation Textures (Train, Lights, Rails):	sbst_atxt
Common:	rock_atx, trash_atxt, storm_atxt

